'From Squeak3.7alpha of ''11 September 2003'' [latest update: #5604] on 12 December 2003 at 3:11:23 pm'!"Change Set:		CleanupUpdateServers-dewDate:			9 December 2003Author:			Doug WayRemove uiuc update url (from Utilities class>>updateUrlLists) which has been defunct for a long time.  Also clean up various other ServerDirectory update servers.  This includes removing the internal/SqC/test update servers; they can be handled with the changeset that adds internal/SqC update visibility."| publicUpdateServers serversToRemove theinternetoneServer |"Remove uiuc update url.  Only the squeakfoundation (internetone) updateUrl will exist as a public (non-European) updateUrl."publicUpdateServers _ Utilities updateUrlLists detect: [:ea | ea first = 'Squeak Public Updates'] ifNone: [nil].publicUpdateServers ifNotNil: [publicUpdateServers at: 2 put: {'update.squeakfoundation.org/external/'}]."Remove all internal/SqC and internetone servers"serversToRemove _ (ServerDirectory serversInGroupNamed: 'SqC Internal Updates*') asOrderedCollection.serversToRemove addAll:	(ServerDirectory servers values asOrderedCollection select: [:ea | ea server = 'ftp.theinternetone.net']).ServerDirectory servers	keysAndValuesRemove: [:key :value | serversToRemove includes: value]."Re-add only the public theinternetone server"theinternetoneServer _ ServerDirectory new.theinternetoneServer	server: 'ftp.theinternetone.net';	directory: 'html/external/updates';	type: #ftp;	user: 'jto19449';	groupName: 'Squeak Public Updates';	altUrl: 'http://update.squeakfoundation.org/external/'.ServerDirectory addServer: theinternetoneServer named: 'UpdatesAtSqF'."Remove various other obsolete update servers"ServerDirectory removeServerNamed: 'UpdatesExtUIUC' ifAbsent: [].ServerDirectory removeServerNamed: 'UpdatesExtUIUC2' ifAbsent: [].ServerDirectory removeServerNamed: 'UpdatesAtSqueak.org' ifAbsent: [].!